Class LocalPlayer

Wrapper for the native LocalPlayer class extending Player and adding some new methods associated specifically with the client-side player entity.

You can construct new LocalPlayer from an existing Actor, Mob or Player, or call Actor.asLocalPlayer.

First will throw java.lang.IllegalArgumentException, second will return null, if given Actor, Mob or Player is not a LocalPlayer.

since

2.0
